legacy.description: 1st Arab, African woman to lead UN Office at Vienna/ Office on Drugs & Crime @UNODC. Proud mother & grandmother, ⚽ fan who stands for fair play in life for all.
legacy.name: GhadaFathiWaly

legacy.full_text:
I was honoured to address the Clean Silk Road Thematic Forum today in Beijing.
 
A Silk Road clean of corruption helps drive forward our #GlobalGoals.
 
Let's stand #UnitedAgainstCorruption to end impunity & protect the integrity of all global efforts for sustainable development. https://t.co/oS7pE2OfJH

Thanks to @Ghadafathiwaly for your contribution to the Thematic Forum on #CleanSilkRoad. China stands ready to work with all countries to strengthen anti-corruption cooperation and contribute to high-quality development of #BeltandRoad cooperation.
